    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蒸汽朋克</h2>《Steam Punks》是一款动作平台游戏，继承了 SNES 版《洛克人 X》等复古传奇的风格。<br>控制马刺市长精英执法者邓斯·卡尔汉 (Dunns Calhan)，对抗臭名昭著的鲍勒帮 (Bowler Gang)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7821b0cd6224f8467f0363bcd1006e6b.poster.avif?t=1769551889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7821b0cd6224f8467f0363bcd1006e6b.webm?t=1769551889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7821b0cd6224f8467f0363bcd1006e6b.mp4?t=1769551889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>钩炮！用它来拖动大箱子+从挂钩点摆动！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7c9e661612453c875bf6aa0f6e1c51d2.poster.avif?t=1769551889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7c9e661612453c875bf6aa0f6e1c51d2.webm?t=1769551889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388420/extras/7c9e661612453c875bf6aa0f6e1c51d2.mp4?t=1769551889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>* 8 个主要关卡，有洛克人风格的 Boss<br>*大量可解锁的物品和能量提升<br>*在 May 的商店查找食谱，学习为 Dunns 的炼金枪制作强力炮弹并升级其威力<br>*通过探索城镇来解锁秘密区域和关卡<br>*以及更多！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >首款 Megamanvinia 类型游戏 </h2>当你解锁物品时，你可以返回关卡以到达新的区域和秘密！<br>洛克人银河恶魔城终极融合！",
